{"lastModified":1774002341672,"uri":"c::8196907601::vessel::d5cc7879-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Gulet","Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nIf you are looking to charter a yacht that can accommodate a large group of friends Tajna Mora is your first choice, offering every luxury you would expect of a yacht of this class. She marries traditional design with exceptional facilities.\n\nFollowing her extensive 2018 refit, her elegant décor, deck space, and entertainment equipment have made her a popular charter yacht. She accommodates 18 guests in 9 cabins, all of them beautifully maintained with en-suite bathrooms. There are 4 double bed cabins + 4 twin bed cabins on the lower deck plus one convertible (double bed or twin bed) cabin on the main deck. Cabins are of excellent size, with enough wardrobe space. Tajna Mora exudes an effortless finesse and offers equal comfort to all members of the group.\n\nThe deck is perfect for socializing and has a nicely designed layout. Tajna Mora offers sun-pads, multiple built-in sofas, and shaded area, and a wide range of water toys. In addition, the design incorporates an extended swimming platform for easier access to the sea.","blueprint":{"name":"TAJNA MORA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7879-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::115c29c0-ab2f-11ef-afd5-216d4a3ca315/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7879-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::114b87f0-ab2f-11ef-afd4-216d4a3ca315/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7879-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::114ebc40-ab2f-11ef-aad0-7dc19cee3a92/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7879-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::11585930-ab2f-11ef-8325-f9ab7245ae55/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7879-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::114d0e90-ab2f-11ef-ae4b-8d8b3e7d6d12/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7879-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::1155