ia::image::a::vessel::d5cc7879-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::115488a0-ab2f-11ef-bee3-abac96000e8f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7879-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::11510630-ab2f-11ef-ae4b-8d8b3e7d6d12/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7879-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::1154fdd0-ab2f-11ef-8323-f9ab7245ae55/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7879-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::114ff4c0-ab2f-11ef-990f-43cd81b9e526/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7879-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::1152daf0-ab2f-11ef-afd4-216d4a3ca315/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7879-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::114c7250-ab2f-11ef-bee1-abac96000e8f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7879-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::1154afb0-ab2f-11ef-8325-f9ab7245ae55/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7879-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::1152daf0-ab2f-11ef-ae4b-8d8b3e7d6d12/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7879-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::114d35a0-ab2f-11ef-afd4-216d4a3ca315/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7879-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::115524e0-ab2f-11ef-aad0-7dc19cee3a92/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7879-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::114bd610-ab2f-11ef-ae4b-8d8b3e7d6d12/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7879-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::115bb490-ab2f-11ef-afd5-216d4a3ca315/{imageVariant}"],"make":"Custom","model":"","maxCrew":6,"sleeps":18,"basePort":{"uri":"a::place::27c28dba-b3ee-11ed-9755-325096b39f47","name":"Split","coordinates":{"latitude":43.51359615,"longitude":16.43884676},"country":"Croatia"},"cruisingCapacity":0,"builtYear":2007,"refitYear":2018,"topSpeed":11,"cruiseSpeed":9,"fuelCapacity":0,"cabinLayout":[{"label":"Convertible Cabin","value":"1"},{"label":"Double Cabin","value":"4"},{"label":"Twin Cabin","value":"4"}],"cabins":9,"bathrooms":0,"length":31,"beam":7.5,"draft":2.6,"hullType":"","hullConstruction":"Steel","tonnage":0,"superStructure":[],"engines":"2 x DOOSAN L086TIH, 420 kW","amenities":[{"label":"Air Conditioning"},{"label":"Deck Shower","quantity":""},{"label":"Hairdryers"},{"label":"Ice Maker"},{"label":"BBQ"}],"toys":[{"label":"Water Skis Adult"},{"label":"Wave Runners hp"},{"label":"Snorkel Gear (For Adults & Children)"},{"label":"Wake Board"},{"label":"Kayaks 1 Pax","quantity":"2"},{"label":"Swim Platform"},{"label":"SUP (Stand Up Paddle Boards)","quantity":"2"},{"label":"Donut"}],"entertainment":["Salon Stereo","Salon TV","Onboard WIFI"],"tenders":["Tender 5.6 m, 70 HP"]},"crew":[{"name":"LUKA JAKIR","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7879-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::8bd8b2c0-ab2c-11ef-9d01-f1366c58cd6f/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Last season holds special significance for Luka as he fulfilled his long term goal of becoming a captain. Now with a successful season under his belt as a captain and following 15 years of dedicated service in the maritime industry he eagerly anticipates next season. From a young age, he's been immersed in the sea, learning the ropes alongside his brother and the crew. Currently studying at the Faculty of Maritime Studies, Luka is committed to delivering top-notch service, prioritizing guest satisfaction above all else. That is a principle he\nupholds with unwavering commitment. Collaborating with the crew,\nhe aims to elevate the onboard experience, striving for excellence\nwith each voyage. Beyond his duties onboard, Luka harbors a\nprofound enthusiasm for automobiles and motorcycles, finding joy in\nexploring the intricacies of engines and the thrill of the open road.\nAdditionally, he loves sports, particularly football, which serves as a source of camaraderie and recreation in his leisure time."},{"name":"KATE MANDALINIC","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::8196907601::vessel::d5cc7879-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::1d411d80-05a7-11f1-9ba7-537447979a95/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Kate is a hardworking and friendly professional with over three years of experience in the hospitality industry. Her background includes working as a waitress in high-volume settings and assisting with the management of her family's bar, where she handled shift coordination and stock management. These roles have equipped her with the essential skills to remain calm under pressure, excel in a team environment, and maintain a guest-first service orientation. New to yachting, Kate is organized, highly adaptable, and a quick learner, eager to apply her proven service and operational skills as a Stewardess."},{"name":"TONI SMOLJANOVIC","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::8196907601::vessel::d5cc7879-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::38efe840-05a7-11f1-9ba7-537447979a95/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Toni is a dedicated and experienced Deckhand with a strong background in maritime work since 2015, building nearly a decade of sea experience. He has a solid reputation as a reliable and hardworking crew member. His recent experience includes working aboard the luxury yachts M/Y Maxita (2024) and M/Y Life is Good (2023). Fluent in English, Toni is a valuable team player known for his positive attitude, strong work ethic, and ability to quickly adapt to new environments, ensuring a smooth onboard operation."},{"name":"IVAN KLISMANIC","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7879-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::f0d629e0-ab2d-11ef-90e0-d56e01c59334/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"When you step on board Tajna Mora and Ivan welcomes you and hands you your first drink you’ll know right then that you are in great hands and your holiday can begin. His philosophy is that each crew member should want and know what is best for the guest at any given time. After going to hospitality school and working in different bars and restaurants he wanted to try something new so he chose to work on the boats because he enjoys meeting new people and presenting traditional food and drinks to guests. Opposite to restaurants, he has more time to prepare the service and dedicate his attention to each person individually. He’s been on “Tajna Mora” for 6 years now, and outside the season, when he is not on guests’ constant beck and call he loves spending time with his family and enjoys sports, especially football."},{"name":"MATEA VIDAKOVIC","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::8196907601::vessel::d5cc7879-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::4ea99550-05a7-11f1-9ba7-537447979a95/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Matea is a professional focused on ensuring a perfect guest experience through proactive service and meticulous attention to detail. She achieves high customer service standards by employing personalized gestures that prioritize guest comfort. Matea is highly valued for her exceptional speed, resourcefulness, and effective collaboration within the crew. She excels in maintaining an unwavering commitment to the highest service standards, thriving in the focused atmosphere of a smaller yacht team. She consistently brings sustained energy and professionalism to every aspect of the charter service."},{"name":"TONI STANKOVIC","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::8196907601::vessel::d5cc7879-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::91f5fa10-05a7-11f1-9ba7-537447979a95/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Toni is a highly motivated hospitality professional with eight years of experience gained in various bars and restaurants. He possesses excellent English skills. While new to the yachting industry, Toni is a quick adaptor who thrives in dynamic, service-oriented environments. He is dedicated to delivering warm, attentive, and genuinely welcoming service, focused on ensuring exceptional guest comfort. He brings an energetic and positive spirit to his role and is eager to expand his experience within the yachting secto